stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: OverlayForegroundService<br/>onCreate
    
    Idle --> Listening: User holds button
    Listening --> Classifying: Button released /<br/>Speech recognized
    Listening --> Error: SpeechRecognizer<br/>error
    Listening --> Timeout: 10s no speech<br/>detected
    
    Classifying --> Saved: AI finishes<br/>in <4s
    Classifying --> Classifying: Transcript<br/>live forward
    Classifying --> Error: AI timeout<br/>7s limit
    
    Saved --> Idle: Auto-dismiss<br/>1000ms fade
    Error --> Idle: Auto-dismiss<br/>2000ms
    Timeout --> Idle: Auto-dismiss<br/>2000ms
    
